^Help - Jail
USAGE: .jail ^user
WHERE: ^user^ is somebody you wish to remove from the Talker.
 
Use this command when you want to automatically:

1) Demote a user to the lowest level
2) Move the user into a "jail" room
3) Deny the user from using most normal commands (.tell, .shout, etc.)
4) Make the user log into the jail room at each logon
5) Change the user's description to indicate jailed state

Captain's may not be jailed.  Even by other Captain's.
 
